messages.message: I found the issue. @Sayan recently changed the file diffing from `get_git_diffed_files_not_staged` to `get_git_diffed_files_to_master_ancestor` and that seems to make the system failed to recognize a file has changed. I updated your build_proto.py file and now it works
@Prakhar Sayan fixed this on master actually. Try pulling it again. We should use `get_git_diffed_files_to_master`
Ohh you meant this when you said pull Sayan's changes earlier :face_palm: My bad, I'll pull the latest changes and try again. Thanks!
Haha, got unlucky that you were stuck on the broken commit.
Yeah this should have been checked by me initially.  Apologies for that
